ource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is thought that Kim, 31, did not receive CPR after she collapsed, despite that being reported by some media outlets.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 3.972990459211631e-12, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  Musk, the Tesla chief and owner of X, formerly known as Twitter, told Kim that she should star in an action movie after she went viral on his social media platform.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.137938177893872e-14, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999998890416, \"rank\": 1.1096554976274394e-10, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"score\": 0.7447696845038385, \"rank\": 0.34268705303079444, \"text\": \"Tesla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"